{
  "stem": "18575.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 267.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In-- actually, in 1942, in July, the Germans started a-- the action, as it's called.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were signs posted on the buildings that anyone that would voluntarily report himself to so-called Umschlagplatz, which was a railroad siding attached to the ghetto, would get-- would go-- will be transported to a labor camp for work, and will get, I think, two pounds of bread and margarine.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, first of all, there were thousands, tens of thousand people starving to death.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the food ration, the card that they got-- they-- you were-- legally got for you food ration, was not enough to live on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You didn't die immediately.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You just starve yourself to death with it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Unless you were able to obtain food on the black market, if you had some means, you were dead.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the-- those starving people, thousands of them, for the two pounds of bread, they would volunteer to go to hell.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And thousands volunteered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But later, there was not enough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they started-- the-- the Germans, together with the Polish police, and Ukrainians, and a Jewish militia, which-- that was formed in the ghetto by the Judenrat, by the Jewish-- Jewish leadership there-- on order of the Germans-- help in capturing surrounding blocks and telling everybody to get out by the-- or they gonna be killed, shot.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And unless they work for a German enterprise and could show documents, they were taken.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And families were broken apart.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And people start hiding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, that's where the danger came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My uncle, the one that I lived with, he was a manager of a [NON-ENGLISH] or a-- what's [NON-ENGLISH] in English?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Sweaters.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What is it made of?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Wool?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not wool.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How-- how is it made, it's--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they not woven.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
